Siyavuya ukuba lo msitho uzinyaswe lindwendwe elibalulekileyo, ophumelele iMbasa yabaseTyhini abakwiCandelo lokOngiwa kwaManzi, uNksz Mapule Phokompe waseMahikeng eMntla Ntshona.
