2. IKhabhinethi ivumile ukuba kungeniswe ePalamente imiThetho eyiYona isiSiseko eHlaziyiweyo neThiywe ngokuTsha yeZizwe eziManyeneyo (i-UN) yeNdlela yokuPhathwa kwamaBanjwa (“iMithetho kaNelson Mandela”).
